00:00:05,640 --> 00:00:09,420
Tidal forces play a role in the formation
and destruction of stars.

2
00:00:09,420 --> 00:00:14,129
They are present in all spatial scales:
in planets, comets,

3
00:00:14,129 --> 00:00:19,550
