It is known that tidal forces can deform objects

4
00:00:19,550 --> 00:00:22,360
as large
as galaxies.

5
00:00:22,360 --> 00:00:25,849
We are familiar with the tidal forces on the
Earth

6
00:00:25,849 --> 00:00:32,090
through the periodic motion of the oceans:
the tides, which gave their name to this force.

7
00:00:32,090 --> 00:00:35,300
